Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:10.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:19.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.61,main,Thief 3,0000,0000,0000,,He's so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:01:01.16,main,Thief 2,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:03.48,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,So, how would you like to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:08.88,main,Thief 1,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please spare us! We'll never \Nattack the village again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:11.01,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I won't kill you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:12.04,main,Thief 1,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:13.67,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Because today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.59,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:21.68,main,Thief 1,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:24.73,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Celebrate Marie's birthday with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:26.06,main,Thief 1,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:28.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Rejoice greatly, rejoice \Nwith all your might,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:30.17,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,and then die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:32.62,main,Thief 1,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:52.80,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}The Mirror Mage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:09.08,sign_4456_19_Village_in_the_B,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Village in the Boonies: Hage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:12.75,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.00,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,They sent money again this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.50,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.31,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Are they doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:23.69,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to eat lots of tatoes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:25.01,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:32.02,sign_19920_225_Wizard_King_Gran,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Wizard King\NGrand Magic Knight\N1st-5th Class Senior Magic Knight\N1st-5th Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N1st Class Junior Magic Knight\N2nd Class Junior Magic Knight\N3rd Class Junior Magic Knight\N4th Class Junior Magic Knight\N5th Class Junior Magic Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:29.22,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Yuno became a\Nfirst-class junior Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:32.02,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome! It's only been \Ntwo months since he joined!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.07,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno is the hope of Hage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.13,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,What about Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:40.10,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's trying too hard \Nand being a burden to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.28,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you can come home at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:48.99,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... "Hello, Sister Lily, \Nbrats at the church, and Mayor."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.54,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:55.29,sign_19920_225_Wizard_King_Gran,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Wizard King\NGrand Magic Knight\N1st-5th Class Senior Magic Knight\N1st-5th Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N1st Class Junior Magic Knight\N2nd Class Junior Magic Knight\N3rd Class Junior Magic Knight\N4th Class Junior Magic Knight\N5th Class Junior Magic Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.29,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's also become a \Nthird-class junior Magic Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.17,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:01.42,italics,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I guess Asta's working hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.18,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,To think our Asta is finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:08.51,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you stay healthy, and do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:11.52,sign_5959_41_The_Golden_Dawn_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Dawn's Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.65,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:18.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you moved up to\Nfirst-class junior Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:19.78,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.90,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.03,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.47,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't want you to get too cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:29.03,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I still far surpass you in \Nboth rank and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.43,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.50,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:44.51,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,A little gift from your senior\Nin honor of your promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:48.05,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You sent all of your pay \Nback home, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.02,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus is so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:57.70,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,He was so happy when he heard \Nyou had been promoted
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.77,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,that his glasses were sparkling with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.02,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit smothering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.70,sign_7329_57_Black_Bulls__Bas,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Black Bulls' Base
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:13.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all eyes up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We just got paid, so no work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.71,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:21.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm gonna train real hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.51,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mr. Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.13,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome decision, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.91,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink! The night's still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.25,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Time for second breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.85,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna hit on all the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.45,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean girls? Mountain girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.86,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All the girls meet... me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:47.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Gauche, good job \Nhandling that many guys yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:53.04,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Today's my sister's birthday, so could I have \Nthe next year off, until her next birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:53.98,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:57.49,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bored! I wonder if anyone \Nwill attack the royal capital again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.68,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Maybe I'll attack it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:01.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bigger no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.38,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Your luck with money goes \Nup if you polish gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,None of these guys intend to work at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:12.23,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton Creation Magic: Sheep Cooks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.90,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.98,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You've got tatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:37.14,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I procured the local specialty from my \Nmeal-saving prince's hometown, Hage Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.50,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Dig in, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:45.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dry. Must be full of fiber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.01,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It's so flaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.47,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It completely dried out my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.61,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.49,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:05.57,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My love for my meal-saving prince \Nprovides the best seasoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:10.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should get my \Ngoddess Marie for her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:14.76,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm gonna get all the cuties—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:15.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.39,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:20.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You want to do some gambling, so you \Nwant me to take you into town again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.42,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No, before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:28.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure if it's the fiber working, \Nbut I'm about to hit my limit right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:31.68,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That is the one limit you may not hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.34,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Evil, begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:41.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to find anything to do \Nwhen we get a day off on such short notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:42.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you have some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:47.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you could drop me off \Nsomewhere on your super-awesome broom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:53.36,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say no to my cute little underling.\NWhere do you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,To Nean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.87,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.71,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The place where those guys had the mixer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.42,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you gonna do there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:08.00,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.66,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:14.73,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I care what he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.76,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-And I have absolutely no interest \Nin who he's going to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.93,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Get on. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.01,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, we're not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:27.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:37.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, so I {\i1}do{\i0} want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:43.75,sign_12510_122_City_in_the_Comm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(751,1)}City in the Common Realm: Nean
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:49.75,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,To my dear, beloved little sister Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:53.26,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I just arrived in the city you live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:58.41,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My job as a Magic Knight is rough, but if\Nit's for you, it's not really rough at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.52,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I can even buy you presents with my pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:15.61,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,A former convict like myself is\Nonly able to live a proper life
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:21.59,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,for the sake of your angelic cuteness, \NMarie. It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.89,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, already, my nose won't stop bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:28.79,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.79,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:35.30,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,Come in! We've got plenty of birthday \Npresents for you to choose from!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.20,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and show me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:38.82,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.61,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,First up, we have these!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:44.15,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,All little girls love plushies, \Nand plushies love little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.81,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure her delight will\Nshow in her angelic smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.32,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.06,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll take them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.07,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.47,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:03.79,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the little darling will enjoy \Nher days playing house as she fantasizes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:06.53,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,about living in a mansion like \Nthis with her beloved brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.59,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.09,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.85,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:19.93,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:24.81,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,Lastly, we have this! With this outfit, \Nyour little sister can be a real angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.86,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:30.94,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Give me everything in the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.98,main,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:46.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're going to see a \Nchick you met at the mixer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:51.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! I promised Rebecca that I would \Nplay with her little siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:56.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,M-Man, you're already meeting \Nher family? Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.80,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.06,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:05.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm going to play \Nwith all the strength I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:07.77,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:20.53,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,To my dear, beloved little sister Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:24.57,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive your brother for \Nbeing late due to his anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:31.21,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I bought you lots of birthday \Npresents. Please be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:36.30,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I used up all of my pay, but no\N price is too high for Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:41.59,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I will be able to see my \Nlittle angel Marie soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:46.34,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to see her smile... \NOh, my beloved Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:49.10,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie... Marie... Ma—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that, Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:01.17,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun! You're so strong, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:03.73,main,Pim,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:04.82,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Are you read—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.00,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her this instant, you trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're my senior with the sister complex\Nwho's always getting nosebleeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:19.37,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me a guy with a sister complex \Nand nosebleeds, meathead runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.71,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stomp you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:24.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I train hard, so you'll have \Nto try harder than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.18,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,He's so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:32.14,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only able to see my sister,\Nwho lives at the church, once a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.25,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the one day that I get \Nto release my pent-up feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:38.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,worship the heck out of my sister, \Nand do all kinds of things with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,so why are you worshiping her first, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See? You do have a sister \Ncomplex and a nosebleed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:47.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So wait, she's your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.93,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare point at my angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.11,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I showed you her picture before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:58.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I was just visiting Rebecca, \Nand she just happened to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:12:59.71,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.85,main,Pim,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.13,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean by "all kinds of things"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.14,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:07.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Marie sure is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:13.23,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she is! More importantly, why \Ndo you have your eye on my little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:15.44,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.03,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be so mean, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:20.73,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to marry him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.98,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to marry him... I'm going to \Nmarry him... I'm going to marry him....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.38,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Marry him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:38.00,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up following him because I was \Ncurious, but what the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:41.00,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Um... May I ask for the fare now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.46,italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.76,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you... I'll kill you... I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:47.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.34,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you... I'll kill you... I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.21,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.71,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Reflect Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck's up with that spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.74,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.03,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.74,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is noisy out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:19.21,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, it's time. We must \Ngo back to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:20.48,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.33,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.41,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you came, Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.50,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.47,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "old hag," it's "Sister."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.66,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's about to go on a date with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.68,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the church by \Nyourself, Sister Old Hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.04,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening. It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.48,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You go home, you sister complex punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:42.98,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's not good for Marie \Nto spend time with a guy like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:47.99,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Your attitude's always terrible. You have\Nmean eyes and a filthy mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.81,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, you shitty old hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:50.77,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,See? Filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:51.99,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.06,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve, \Nsaying that to an old lady
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:57.18,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,who's not long for this world, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right, dumbass. \NSays the old she-demon who'll
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.04,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,probably live another hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:04.17,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to people like \Nthey're monsters, you thug!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.96,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, gangster hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How can you talk to your elders like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:14.35,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.12,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.45,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:20.58,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, Asta! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:26.28,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.11,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:28.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, sister complex guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:32.50,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,M-Ma... Ma... Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.50,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,What a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:40.37,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come in and have dinner at\Nour place while you wait for him to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.82,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to spend \Nthe night... if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:45.86,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:46.88,main,Pim,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.47,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Spend the night?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:54.31,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to spend the night at the home \Nof a girl he just met?! Is he stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.97,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid can he be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:59.58,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,And Asta is so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.40,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,That really loud boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.55,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:09.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,S...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.35,main,Pim,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.05,main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some moguro fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.62,main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:27.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All these dishes are so good \Nthat I can't put my spoon down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.41,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be a great wife one day, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.31,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:42.64,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?! There's more to\Nbeing a good wife than just being a good cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.69,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Sissy, are you going to marry Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:55.45,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:59.01,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:05.96,main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,You should totally jump him tonight, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.12,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! What are you saying, Luca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:13.92,main,Pem,0000,0000,0000,,Goo goo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:17.14,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You too, Pem?! Do you even \Nknow what you're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:21.65,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jump him? No, you dummy, dummy, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.16,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:39.66,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even winter! Why is it so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:24.70,flashback,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,You should totally jump him tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.72,flashback,Pem,0000,0000,0000,,Goo goo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:26.96,flashback,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You too, Pem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:30.39,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! Dummy, dummy, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:33.21,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I-I would never do anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:40.43,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm just going to check and see if \NLuca and Marco are actually asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.54,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.90,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Reflect Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gauche?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Wait, what? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:33.98,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to marry Marie. I'll make \Nsure it doesn't happen by killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Kids say stuff like that all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Only cowards attack people in their sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:48.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it's cowardly or not,\Nas long as I can kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.25,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:52.95,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Real Double.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.27,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now there are two Gauches?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:59.59,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,First he shoots beams out of a mirror,\Nand now this? What's up with his magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.59,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Your crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:04.43,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,is the fact that you met my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:08.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that make most people criminals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.18,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not even your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:29.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,S-Snow? When did it pile up so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even the season for that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:34.39,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that. Just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:38.21,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you two think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:41.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.20,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:45.30,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.55,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Urian, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:50.06,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:50.89,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.06,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Von is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:16.33,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:18.57,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,you're all my friends.
