Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:56.66,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:23:00.85,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Double Gauche
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:22:59.33,main,gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Double Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:02.98,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:05.55,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Spin me around like Asta did!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:10.74,sign_33285_329_I_ll____kill_him,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... kill him!!
